n-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.22.04-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.43.40-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.36.46-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.34.59-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.38.15-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.17.51-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.38.15-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.30.20-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.30.20-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.34.59-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.17.51-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/FuzzieMints.gif", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.35.24-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.30.20-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.38.15-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.36.46-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.25.13-AM.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png"], "content": "<p>Your own OnCyber Gallery requires no picture hooks, no frames...and crucially, no permission to open. Start creating your OnCyber gallery with as little as a handful of collected or created artworks. Here are five reasons to help your art get seen by collectors and fans.</p><p><strong>TL:DR OnCyber Artist Opportunities</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Immersion. </strong>OnCyber immerses your in the art and almost certainly 'hits different' to an OpenSea thumbnail. </li><li><strong>Signal sale success. A sold out OnCyber Gallery</strong> can show newer collectors what people already value.</li><li><strong>Curate yourself. </strong>Your collection is more see as a sum of its parts and you know it.</li><li><strong>Curate and show a group of collaboration of artists</strong> with a similar style. Create a lightning road for attention amongst Kerala photographers, Crypto Aesthetic or GAN specialists. It's easier to buy many than one ;)</li><li><strong>Free your art from Tezos blockchain friction</strong> and<strong> </strong>Create an OnCyber Gallery of work for sale. </li></ol><p><strong>Art is meant to be seen and shared. </strong></p><h3 id=\"1-immersion\">1. Immersion</h3><p>Art is meant to be experienced and felt. Your iPhone13 is amazing yes... but get out the tape measure and tell me your collectors are getting the full impact from a 6.7 inch sized JPEG. Immerse your potential collectors in an OnCyber space starts with say 20 artworks you feel are worthy of a collection. </p><p>There are four free templates, white cube being my favourite for its refined simplicity though I wish there were four more places to add art at each end of the gallery. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1850\" height=\"952\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.40.27-AM.png 1850w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Create your first <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/create\">OnCyber gallery</a>.</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"2-signal-sale-success\">2. Signal Sale Success</h3><p>After you've had some success selling NFT's, consider a show of SOLD OUT work. Yes, why not? After all... it's not hard to discover what art is still available thanks to your well laid out Twitter LinkTree and direct link to Foundation or SuperRare (I hope:)</p><p>Showing a collection of SOLD OUT art takes an extra step and OnCyber has got you covered. You'll need to ask the owner of your art to share their NFT for you to curate. Not hard, and not a security risk... and pretty cool. OnCyber enabling the metaverse to do super cool stuff again.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.34.59-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"984\" height=\"516\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.34.59-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.34.59-AM.png 984w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"3-curate-yourself\">3. Curate Yourself</h3><p>Creating a collection that is greater together than a sum of its parts, is the grail of gallery curation. Artists feel something in each work...and also might know how to best translate that collectively. Curating your own OnCyber gallery opens up the possibility for collectors to feel what you feel about the collection in aggregate. Cohesion is more apparent in a gallery space... </p><p>OnCyber helps your art talk amongst itself and tell a combined story.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.43.40-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"823\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.43.40-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.43.40-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.43.40-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-10.43.40-AM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>MintFace <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetic-moments\">Geodetic Moments</a> landscapes look better OnCyber than OpenSea</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"4-curate-through-collaboration\">4. Curate Through Collaboration</h3><p>Consider the <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/6529gm\">gm gallery</a> created by the artist community, funded by Punk6529 and curated by MintFace. It is a curation of how we as a community collectively celebrate gm. Anybody can create an OnCyber gallery around a theme that matters to the collective. Here's five themes that I'd love to see to help the next tranche of collectors make purchasing decisions.</p><p>1) Glitch / Crypto art<br />2) Generative art (outside of Art Blocks)<br />3) Mental Health art (the darkness and the light)<br />4) High school talent<br />5) 100 hour + work per NFT gallery<br />5) Lens based specifically .MP4</p><p>Moving images on a digital wall bring the digital space alive in a way still images can't. MintFace is a fan.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/FuzzieMints.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2670\" height=\"1430\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/fuzziemints\">FuzzieMints</a> feature in <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/afterlife\">The Afterlife</a> Gallery</figcaption></figure><p>There are plenty more...unlimited ways of collaborating to bring bigger attention to your art. Instagram may have divided artists ability to naturally cocreate...now you get to reclaim collaboration for everyone to benefit. OnCyber unlocks the power of collaboration for you. </p><h3 id=\"5-free-your-tezos-art-with-oncyber\">5. Free your Tezos Art with OnCyber</h3><p>Art collectors are slowed down on the Tezos blockchain because its slow and frustrating. Slow costs you sales. Yes, artists enjoy the low cost gas of living is the Tezos blockchain suburbs, but you've also gotta be content with being far from the downtown buzz of ethereum. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🍒MintFace HΞN Gallery is open!<a href=\"https://t.co/BuTc4n3BGh\">https://t.co/BuTc4n3BGh</a><br /><br />Thanks <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mattmedved?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mattmedved</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/oncyber_io?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@oncyber_io</a> for the nudge<br /><br />Gallery art (clockwise)<a href=\"https://twitter.com/abidaker?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@abidaker</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/alistairkeddie?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@alistairkeddie</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RoustanNFT?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@RoustanNFT</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_cagritaskin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@_cagritaskin</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PopWonderNFT?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@PopWonderNFT</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zenaranya?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@zenaranya</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gi1771771ck?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gi1771771ck</a> <br />DeHaze<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Pinktofu_art?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Pinktofu_art</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ericreator?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ericreator</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ScottBatemanArt?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ScottBatemanArt<\n/a> <a href=\"https://t.co/SbIJl0fk6Z\">pic.twitter.com/SbIJl0fk6Z</a></p>&mdash; mintface.eth (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1452888514165559296?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 26, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>The Hic et Nunc gallery isn't that easy to navigate for collectors (yet). Twitter and Tezos work well, yet it's hard (<a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/setup-temple-wallet-for-hic-et-nunc/\">Getting Setup on Tez article</a>) to woo collectors when Eth needs to get exchanged for Tezos (XTZ). </p><h3 id=\"oncyber-inspiration\">OnCyber Inspiration</h3><p>There are some very cool collections out there. Here are a few that I recommend your digitally walk around in for the feels.<br /></p><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/6529gm\">6529 gm Gallery</a> - a gallery expressing a kaleidoscope of gm. We the NFT fam.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1167\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.27.40-AM.png 2396w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/6529gm\">6529 gm Gallery</a></figcaption></figure><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/6529photo\">6529 Photo Gallery</a> - 6529's photography gallery representing our NFT era. The considered beauty of the collection is astounding.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.25.13-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1114\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.25.13-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.25.13-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.25.13-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.25.13-AM.png 2398w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/6529photo\">6529 Photo Gallery</a> OnCyber</figcaption></figure><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/krybharat\">Musée d'art Gallery</a> - for its two Lost Robbies, in what might be the lowest key flex curation decision of a gallery yet.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.22.04-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1111\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.22.04-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.22.04-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.22.04-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.22.04-AM.png 2368w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/krybharat\">Bharat Krymo's Musée d'art</a> OnCyber</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"ac-collection\">AC Collection</h3><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/ac_collection\">AC Collection Gallery</a> - for its 'God Mode' Fidenza...and it's beautifully positioned 'A' and 'C' 720 Digitals. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1104\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1600/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w2400/2021/10/Screen-Shot-2021-10-27-at-11.20.29-AM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/ac_collection\">AC Collection Gallery</a> OnCyber</figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"deeze-gallery\">Deeze Gallery</h3><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/deeze\">Deeze Gallery</a> for its psychedelic brilliance that lands me somewhere on the beaches of Koh Phangan, flat out with my CryptoPunk friends.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2021/